    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2010 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) is a superlative example of the marque's engineering pinnacle. Featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six, this naturally aspirated power plant delivers a linear 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with PASM for adaptive damping and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and turn-in response. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the finish remains flawless under a multi-stage ceramic coating. Mechanical integrity is absolute, with zero bore scoring and a pristine undercarriage, representing a true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
